{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was a normal [LAUGHS] Hungarian family and nothing very romantic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that's-- that-- that was-- I had lots cousins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "None-- excepting one, none-- none of the others were touched by anything, because they, the-- [SIGHS] the men and the women, married out of-- out of the-- the Jewish religion entirely.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And if you were half-Jewish and married a non-Jew, then you weren't you know, you-- you weren't considered to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- one, as I said, one cousin was, and she died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she-- she died in Auschwitz and so did her mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they're the only-- But, then, there were some aunts of my father's who-- who-- who were taken.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Aunt, one aunt of my father's was taken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because of being Jewish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, because of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's-- that's how-- but whether they were actually Jewish or not, I don't know, because they didn't live in Pecs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know that they were, because she married a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, of course, they were taken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was what one-- I guess one would call a-- a physician, an internalist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he specialized in thyroid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Incredible coincidence, you know, my grandmother having died of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was-- that's was-- that's what was his specialty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he did a lot of research.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he-- he was-- by the time he died, he was a-- an accepted and recognized world authority on thyroid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even-- even after the war, we-- we had-- we got a-- one of the medical papers-- medical journals from America was actually quoting him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother, my God, when she saw that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, one of his books, quoted from one of his books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and also, the-- she-- he-- Oxford University was actually looking for him.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
